data.description: Motivated Seller! Looking for convenience and low maintenance living? This end unit Valleybrook Park townhouse offers this and so much more! Everyone will have privacy with each bedroom's full ensuite bathroom and a large walk in closet. The generous kitchen and breakfast room are perfect for meal prep and gathering with family and friends. On these cooler evenings, cozy up to the gas fireplace in the living room. The separate dining with a bay window could be used as a flex room or a home office. The full size laundry room completes this main level. Upstairs is a very large bedroom with its own full bathroom and another large walk in closet. Two generous walk out attic spaces offer more than enough storage.  Privacy abounds in the back with beautiful trees and an installed gas grill. The large utility room off of the covered back porch is perfect for gardening tools or other needed walkout storage. HVAC was updated approximately in 2021, and windows were installed in 2012. Make your appointment to see this wonderful property before it's gone!
